I know not everybody has Twitter searches for mentions of Uncorked, but saw this guy from Poland today post this in response to Jenny's continued popular Angular post: 

"Huge thank you Jenny for: Multipart/form-data File Upload with AngularJS <http://uncorkedstudios.com/blog/multipart…|uncorkedstudios.com/blog/multipart…> via @UncorkedStudios - exactly what i needed"
